data.description: Newer home for sale! Built in 2017 along the end of a private cul-de-sac, this home presents four spacious upstairs bedrooms, all but one has walk-in closets!  The primary floor offers a great room to host friends.  The kitchen space uses the open concept design hunkered down by an oversized island.  The double car garage and driveway provides enough parking for four vehicles. Outside mountain views are not to be missed.  Enjoy the views as you travel to local restaurants and shopping outlets minutes from this home, common commute to JBLM!
